Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:04.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 初次见面 尾崎医生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:10.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:14.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后我哥哥也会来 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他什么袭击尾崎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:37.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结城君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:46.98,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛し…愛し合うのさ もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:46.98,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱…更加地相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:53.24,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}激しい渇きに狂いそう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:53.24,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}激烈的饥渴让我发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:01:02.43,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}目を閉じて 罪深き くちづけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:01:02.43,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闭上眼睛 罪孽深重的接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:13.19,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}お前の匂い 狂わせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:13.19,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你的味道 令人发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:17.15,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真夜中に目覚めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:17.15,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在半夜里睁开眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:20.18,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}狂気 愛 飲み干す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:20.18,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}把爱与疯狂喝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:23.53,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}おいでこの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:23.53,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}过来 到我的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:26.65,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「あっちの闇は苦いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:26.65,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「那边的黑暗是苦涩的」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:32.60,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の惑い 揺らめく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:32.60,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你在迷惘 在动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:36.19,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて永遠になる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:36.19,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}最终将永远无法解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:39.55,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「こっちの闇は甘いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:39.55,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「这边的黑暗是甘甜的」
